      "originalText": "Chain of Thought \n- Distribute your computation cross many tokens\n- Modelos tem problemas em contar números\n- ask model to create intermediate answers or tool results.\n- use steps as tools \"<WRITE_BYTE>0x2c62</WRITE_BYTE>\n<finite-time-deterministic-execution>Hello world</f-t-d-e>\n<assistant>:\"",
